      <p class="grey-text text-darken-3 lighten-3">and knew there were others who felt the same way? Welcome to VoteForLaughs - where you can join with other like-minded comedy fans to encourage the biggest and best comedians to come perform in your town or city. Or, encourage the local club to book an up and coming comedian whose podcast you can't get enough of by adding your city to their page and encouraging others to vote it up. You can also opt in to notifications when your favorite comedians add a show close by so you don't miss out on tickets. With VoteForLaughs, it's all just a few clicks away!</p>
    </div>

